{"tid":22152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【朱仔成】《Rainbow Six》增香港飛虎隊　網民倡休班警列恐怖份子","createTime":"2016-12-04T09:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T17:10:14.000Z","uid":11001,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e57881a800eadb7eaa7cb2e67ed80ae4bbc3abf8","tid":22152,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T09:16:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/15369203_842672132501897_8102484829929375844_o_lJ6Iq_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F15369203_842672132501897_8102484829929375844_o_lJ6Iq_1200x0.jpg&h=edcb8afc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n射擊遊戲《虹彩六號：圍攻行動》（Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Siege）宣布，即將在遊戲中推加新元素，新增香港「飛虎隊」的角色。不過香港網民似乎對此更新頗反感，有人留言揶揄香港警察的技能應是「暗角打鑊」，亦有人提議將休班警列入恐怖分子陣營。<br />\n<br />\n《虹彩六號：圍攻行動》去年12月已經發行，不過遊戲商Ubisoft今日在Facebook宣布，遊戲將新增4個特勤單位陣容，包含有「飛虎隊」之稱的香港警察特警隊。遊戲中香港將聯同西班牙、波蘭以及南韓展開反恐任務。<br />\n<br />\n該帖文一出即引來網民熱論，不少網民重提多宗香港警員涉嫌濫暴的事件。有網民提議「新增技能：暗角打獲」、「新增武器：87連裝催淚彈、特大裝胡椒噴霧、對學生防暴手套」、「解鎖武器：朱經瑋警棍」。有人則留言道「恐怖分子方面建議可以新增休班警」，揶揄近期休班警屢涉各式罪案。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/rainbow-six-增香港飛虎隊-網民揶揄應設-暗角-技能-倡休班警列恐怖份子/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Frainbow-six-%E5%A2%9E%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A3%9B%E8%99%8E%E9%9A%8A-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%8F%B6%E6%8F%84%E6%87%89%E8%A8%AD-%E6%9A%97%E8%A7%92-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD-%E5%80%A1%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%88%97%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E4%BB%BD%E5%AD%90%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=59db6970\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Frainbow-six-%E5%A2%9E%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A3%9B%E8%99%8E%E9%9A%8A-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%8F%B6%E6%8F%84%E6%87%89%E8%A8%AD-%E6%9A%97%E8%A7%92-%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD-%E5%80%A1%E4%BC%91%E7%8F%AD%E8%AD%A6%E5%88%97%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E4%BB%BD%E5%AD%90%2F&h=49e5cfb4\" target=\"_blank\">ht